Package: sybil
Title: Lung Cancer Risk Preduction with Sybil
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew T.", "Warkentin", , "matthew.warkentin@ucalgary.ca", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides an R interface to 'Sybil', a Python-based neural network
    for lung cancer prediction from low-dose computed tomography (LDCT) scans.
    This package enables users to run Sybil models and integrate LDCT-based
    lung cancer risk prediction workflows within R.
